B.LW=new A.cs("The Rule","Normal MUAPs have 2-4 phases. >4 phases is considered polyphasic.")
B.LE=new A.cs("The Standard","Up to 10% of MUAPs can be polyphasic in completely healthy muscle. Don't overcall it.")
B.M_=new A.cs("The Sound","A higher-frequency, somewhat 'clicky' or 'scratchy' sound due to the rapid baseline crossings.")
B.LO=new A.cs("The Significance","It is simply a measure of desynchronization. It does NOT distinguish between neuropathy and myopathy.")
